+++ autofs-5.1.7/CHANGELOG
@@ -102,6 +102,7 @@
 - bailout on rpc systemerror.
 - fix nfsv4 only mounts should not use rpcbind.
 - dont use initgroups() at spawn.
+- fix invalid tsv access.
 
